<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 14:08:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡禁止半岛电视台，因为他只想听到他的声音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-banned-al-jazeera-because-he-wants-only-his-voice-to-be-heard/0000018f-7c0c-d0be-a7bf-fe6e68650000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府决定禁止半岛电视台及其对新闻自由的漠视并不令人意外。这是徒劳的、危险的和反民主的。但关闭不会阻止我们对加沙战争双方的报道</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 13:32:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-banned-al-jazeera-because-he-wants-only-his-voice-to-be-heard/0000018f-7c0c-d0be-a7bf-fe6e68650000</guid></item><item><title>否认、蔑视和非人化：为什么加沙战争意味着以色列现在必须承认大灾难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/denial-and-dehumanization-why-the-gaza-war-means-israel-must-now-acknowledge-the-nakba/0000018f-7bd1-d430-a38f-fff5a8300000</link><description>当内塔尼亚胡政府的部长们威胁要发生“第二次灾难”时，同时拒绝承认 1948 年第一次驱逐巴勒斯坦人，当他们抹去绿线并声称加沙没有无辜人民时，被切断与他们的联系的不仅仅是巴勒斯坦人。根源，也是以色列人</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 13:23:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/denial-and-dehumanization-why-the-gaza-war-means-israel-must-now-acknowledge-the-nakba/0000018f-7bd1-d430-a38f-fff5a8300000</guid></item><item><title>以色列轰炸加沙时，一名巴勒斯坦人和一名以色列人帮助加沙人建造更安全的避难所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-israel-bombs-gaza-a-palestinian-and-an-israeli-help-gazans-build-safer-shelters/0000018f-7b7e-dd4f-ab8f-fffee6100000</link><description>居住在德国的一名加沙人和一名以色列人为流离失所的加沙人筹集了基本基础设施的捐款，并已经建造了一个营地，为数十个家庭提供住所</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 12:59:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-israel-bombs-gaza-a-palestinian-and-an-israeli-help-gazans-build-safer-shelters/0000018f-7b7e-dd4f-ab8f-fffee6100000</guid></item><item><title>尽管禁止悬挂巴勒斯坦旗帜，仍有数十人参加特拉维夫大学的 Nakba 集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/despite-ban-on-palestinian-flags-dozens-join-nakba-rally-at-tel-aviv-university/0000018f-7c15-d604-af8f-7f153f940000</link><description>相反，抗议者挥舞着西瓜形状的标语牌。几十名 Im Tirtzu 活动人士举行了反集会。特拉维夫地区警方将旗帜禁令归因于现在的“敏感时期”</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 12:04:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/despite-ban-on-palestinian-flags-dozens-join-nakba-rally-at-tel-aviv-university/0000018f-7c15-d604-af8f-7f153f940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部召见参加浩劫游行的教师</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-ministry-calls-in-teacher-after-being-photographed-at-nakba-march/0000018f-7bc4-d808-a9bf-fbd792050000</link><description>在学生和家长向学校官员施加压力要求解雇 Sabreen Msarwi 后，教育部表示将寻求澄清此事</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 11:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-ministry-calls-in-teacher-after-being-photographed-at-nakba-march/0000018f-7bc4-d808-a9bf-fbd792050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列古镇的巨型罐子让考古学家困惑不已</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/giant-jars-in-small-ancient-town-in-israel-puzzle-archaeologists/0000018f-7b7b-dd4f-ab8f-ffff331a0000</link><description>Pithoi 在青铜时代的地中海地区曾风靡一时，但当地的制造在青铜时代中期结束时停止了。然后在 Tel Burna 又开始了</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 10:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/giant-jars-in-small-ancient-town-in-israel-puzzle-archaeologists/0000018f-7b7b-dd4f-ab8f-ffff331a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列独立日，以色列国防军士兵在加沙南部被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-on-israels-independence-day/0000018f-7b63-dd07-adbf-fb73b1500000</link><description>中士。 Ira Yair Gispan，19 岁，来自佩塔提克瓦，是 Amit 和 Talia 的儿子，学习软件工程。他过去的老师形容他有“迷人的微笑”，这让老师很难对他生气</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 09:58:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-on-israels-independence-day/0000018f-7b63-dd07-adbf-fb73b1500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外交部透露，持有外交护照的人不到3%</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-ministry-reveals-less-than-3-of-diplomatic-passport-holders/0000018f-7b28-d430-a38f-ffecc5ec0000</link><description>商务部表示，未列出可能危害国家安全、持有人人身安全或对外关系的人员以及未成年人的姓名。亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡 (Yair Netanyahu) 被列入名单，尽管他没有达到入选标准</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 09:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-ministry-reveals-less-than-3-of-diplomatic-passport-holders/0000018f-7b28-d430-a38f-ffecc5ec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列提议：只有在达成协议结束真主党敌对行动后才与黎巴嫩进行边界谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-proposal-border-talks-with-lebanon-only-after-deal-to-end-hezbollah-hostilities/0000018f-78be-d599-ab8f-7cff1cd90000</link><description>贝鲁特渴望尽快就新边界问题展开谈判，但以色列官员宁愿等到战斗结束。根据法律，任何以色列领土的转让都必须进行全民公投——内塔尼亚胡可能很难获得支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 05:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-proposal-border-talks-with-lebanon-only-after-deal-to-end-hezbollah-hostilities/0000018f-78be-d599-ab8f-7cff1cd90000</guid></item><item><title>莎拉·埃尔弗雷斯 (Sarah Elfreth) 赢得马里兰州初选，AIPAC 取得 2024 年最大选举胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/aipac-scores-its-biggest-electoral-victory-of-2024-as-sarah-elfreth-wins-maryland-primary/0000018f-7a3e-dd07-adbf-fb7e65c10000</link><description>埃尔弗雷斯在马里兰州初选中赢得众议院空缺席位，这被认为是亲以色列游说团体急需的路线修正，此前该团体之前在加州的重大投资未能阻止选民选择戴夫·明 (Dave Min)。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 03:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/aipac-scores-its-biggest-electoral-victory-of-2024-as-sarah-elfreth-wins-maryland-primary/0000018f-7a3e-dd07-adbf-fb7e65c10000</guid></item><item><title>正统派政客和以色列国防官员之间的僵局使极端正统派征兵陷入困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/impasse-between-haredi-pols-israeli-defense-chiefs-leaves-ultra-orthodox-draft-in-limbo/0000018f-78ea-d430-a38f-fdee86e40000</link><description>正统派政客坚称，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡政府采取的任何招募计划都将遭到反对，并暗示不同的联盟可以确保为选民提供更好的协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/impasse-between-haredi-pols-israeli-defense-chiefs-leaves-ultra-orthodox-draft-in-limbo/0000018f-78ea-d430-a38f-fdee86e40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：只要哈马斯仍然掌权，讨论加沙的“后天”毫无意义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-live/state-dept-moves-1b-weapons-aid-for-israel-to-congressional-review-u-s-officials-say/0000018f-7a05-d604-af8f-7f05810c0000</link><description>以色列国防军证实真主党战地指挥官在以色列无人机对黎巴嫩南部的袭击中丧生；真主党声称对火箭弹袭击负责 ■ 布林肯称以色列需要针对加沙的“明确而具体的计划” ■ 内塔尼亚胡推进极端正统的以色列国防军征兵法案 ■ 白宫表示，如果国会通过一项关于以色列安全援助的法案，拜登将否决该法案</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 02:18:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-live/state-dept-moves-1b-weapons-aid-for-israel-to-congressional-review-u-s-officials-say/0000018f-7a05-d604-af8f-7f05810c0000</guid></item><item><title>哈佛大学同意讨论中东冲突，学生结束抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/harvard-students-end-protest-as-university-agrees-to-discuss-middle-east-conflict/0000018f-7950-dd07-adbf-fb72a3f60000</link><description>哈佛大学临时校长艾伦·加伯同意就学生的问题举行抗议者和大学官员的会面</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 23:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/harvard-students-end-protest-as-university-agrees-to-discuss-middle-east-conflict/0000018f-7950-dd07-adbf-fb72a3f60000</guid></item><item><title>国防部官员称司法部门拒绝停止对 10 月 7 日事件的调查存在利益冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-cry-conflict-of-interest-over-justices-refusal-to-halt-oct-7-probe/0000018f-78ec-d599-ab8f-7cff5ba00000</link><description>批评者认为，最高法院法官吉拉·坎菲·斯坦尼茨的丈夫、前部长尤瓦尔·斯坦尼茨可能会从国家审计长的调查中受益</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 21:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-cry-conflict-of-interest-over-justices-refusal-to-halt-oct-7-probe/0000018f-78ec-d599-ab8f-7cff5ba00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员警告称，随着危机加剧，埃及可能会退出人质交易调解努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-caution-that-egypt-may-pull-out-of-hostage-deal-mediation-efforts/0000018f-78e2-d7a4-adcf-fcf7cc1c0000</link><description>由于开罗拒绝允许人道主义援助通过拉法口岸，以色列和埃及之间的危机正在加深，以色列官员也担心国防和情报合作可能被降级</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 21:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-caution-that-egypt-may-pull-out-of-hostage-deal-mediation-efforts/0000018f-78e2-d7a4-adcf-fcf7cc1c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列平民在以色列北部被导弹炸死，五名以色列国防军士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-civilian-killed-by-missile-in-northern-israel-five-idf-soldiers-wounded/0000018f-7899-dd07-adbf-fbfbd9200000</link><description>早些时候，火箭弹向马尔基亚地区发射，引发的大火仍在肆虐，其中一枚发射到西加利利的火箭弹击中了一个监视气球，落入黎巴嫩境内</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 20:21:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-civilian-killed-by-missile-in-northern-israel-five-idf-soldiers-wounded/0000018f-7899-dd07-adbf-fbfbd9200000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最令人沮丧的独立日，内塔尼亚胡利用阵亡者和人质进行宣传</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/on-a-wretched-independence-day-netanyahu-exploited-the-fallen-and-hostages-for-propaganda/0000018f-787e-df8f-a78f-fdff759c0000</link><description>以色列总理和他的妻子因胆怯而缺席国家独立日仪式，他们预先录制了一段讲话，其中没有任何承担责任的暗示——所有电视网络都乐于播出，就像现场直播一样</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 20:13:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/on-a-wretched-independence-day-netanyahu-exploited-the-fallen-and-hostages-for-propaganda/0000018f-787e-df8f-a78f-fdff759c0000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙贾巴利亚，没有“后天”战略，以色列士兵再次与哈马斯作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-gazas-jabalya-with-no-day-after-strategy-israeli-soldiers-fight-hamas-again/0000018f-77e6-df8f-a78f-ffff2f2b0000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布四个多月前“解散”了加沙北部的哈马斯营。现在，以色列军队的整个旅已经返回，他们的经历与他们的对手一样</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 17:24:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-gazas-jabalya-with-no-day-after-strategy-israeli-soldiers-fight-hamas-again/0000018f-77e6-df8f-a78f-ffff2f2b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列拒绝讨论加沙战争“第二天”威胁美国的整个中东战略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-14/ty-article/.highlight/israels-refusal-to-discuss-day-after-gaza-war-threatens-americas-mideast-strategy/0000018f-77a3-ddbe-addf-77af6eab0000</link><description>以色列在哈马斯事件后第二天对讨论的顽固态度不仅会危及美国推动进程的努力，而且可能导致大幅倒退，从而产生深远的后果</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 16:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-14/ty-article/.highlight/israels-refusal-to-discuss-day-after-gaza-war-threatens-americas-mideast-strategy/0000018f-77a3-ddbe-addf-77af6eab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 221 天​​：埃及考虑因拉法行动降低与以色列的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-221-egypt-mulls-downgrading-relations-with-israel-over-rafah-op/0000018f-77d2-d430-a38f-f7f640e60000</link><description>国际法院将讨论南非周四针对以色列在拉法的进攻而寻求的新紧急措施 ■ 据报道，拜登政府认为以色列在拉法外集中了足够的兵力，以便在未来几天内进行全面进攻 ■ 卡塔尔总理：就释放人质/停火协议进行谈判由于以色列的拉法行动，局势陷入僵局 ■ 以色列极端分子纵火焚烧了两辆加沙救援卡车 ■ 战争进入 221 天​​后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 16:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-221-egypt-mulls-downgrading-relations-with-israel-over-rafah-op/0000018f-77d2-d430-a38f-f7f640e60000</guid></item></channel></rss>